30:38.703 --> 30:39.570
Oh, wow.

30:39.572 --> 30:42.105
And it's gonna be
what you need to do.

30:42.107 --> 30:45.809
- Okay.
- If you stick with this diet, then do that.

30:45.811 --> 30:47.878
Being at 700 pounds,

30:47.880 --> 30:50.614
you could easily lose
