31:02.094 --> 31:04.928
[Dr. Now] But minimum,
80 pounds in two months,

31:04.930 --> 31:08.665
- and if you do that, then we can work with you.
- Okay.

31:08.667 --> 31:10.367
And if you're not
able to do that,

31:10.369 --> 31:12.269
there's nothing anybody
can do for you.

31:12.804 --> 31:13.804
- Okay.
- Okay?

31:13.806 --> 31:15.105
All right, Ontreon,

31:15.107 --> 31:18.675
so I'm gonna see you in two
months, 80 pounds lighter.

31:18.677 --> 31:20.444
- Okay.
- [Dr. Now] Okay?

31:20.446 --> 31:22.112
- Mmm-hmm.
- So you think you can do that?

31:22.480 --> 31:24.348
I'll do my best.

31:24.350 --> 31:27.951
- All right, if you need anything, give me a call.
- [Ontreon] Okay, I will.

31:27.953 --> 31:29.853
- And thank you so very much.
- [Dr. Now] You're welcome.

31:29.855 --> 31:31.188
Thank you.

31:36.961 --> 31:39.096
- You get the door, baby.
- All righty.

31:41.032 --> 31:43.834
- Let's go.
- Okay.

31:43.836 --> 31:47.337
<i>[Ontreon] I wasn't sure what
to expect from this appointment.</i>

31:47.339 --> 31:50.040
<i>I didn't know if Dr. Now
would even help me.</i>

31:50.042 --> 31:52.142
<i>But now that I met him,</i>

31:52.144 --> 31:55.245
<i>I understand that he just
