32:03.087 --> 32:05.055
<i>He made it sound so easy.</i>

32:05.057 --> 32:08.225
<i>But he's dealing with
a lifetime of habit forming.</i>

32:08.726 --> 32:10.827
<i>It's hard to change that.</i>

