33:27.172 --> 33:30.741
<i>That I need to make things
easier for myself right now.</i>

33:30.743 --> 33:33.010
<i>Because it's hard
enough already.</i>

33:54.866 --> 33:59.536
<i>So far, the diet and exercise
program has been going hot and cold.</i>

34:01.239 --> 34:02.973
<i>But I'm still doing my best.</i>

34:02.975 --> 34:04.941
[groans softly]

34:08.880 --> 34:10.747
<i>My wife Musa
