34:10.749 --> 34:12.983
<i>to give me the right things.</i>

34:12.985 --> 34:17.254
<i>Encouraging me and
staying on top of it with me.</i>

34:17.256 --> 34:20.290
<i>She's even been reading
the materials more than I have.</i>

34:21.492 --> 34:23.026
<i>And for the exercising,</i>

34:23.028 --> 34:25.762
<i>I haven't really done
