39:08.046 --> 39:08.978
[Musa] Oh.

39:09.947 --> 39:12.916
Babe, I don't know
if I came even close.

39:12.918 --> 39:14.584
I don't think I did, you know.

39:14.586 --> 39:17.554
[Musa] You've been
doing the diet.

39:18.589 --> 39:19.823
Yeah.

39:19.825 --> 39:21.858
Yeah, and the other things
we just have to clear up

39:21.860 --> 39:23.960
with them about the shakes.

39:23.962 --> 39:27.230
Because I told you shakes, no.
