39:27.232 --> 39:29.265
It's like we're understanding
it in a different way.

39:29.267 --> 39:30.934
All right.

39:30.936 --> 39:32.235
Yeah, because
at the end of the day

39:32.237 --> 39:34.838
we say different things,
it doesn't help.

39:34.840 --> 39:36.272
[Ontreon] I hear you, baby.

39:41.312 --> 39:43.046
All right, let's go, baby.

39:56.260 --> 39:57.961
Hmm?

40:00.231 --> 40:02.999
So now, not enough of them.

40:04.735 --> 40:06.603
Ontreon?

40:06.605 --> 40:09.506
<i>[Ontreon] Today's the day of
