- Okay.

40:16.982 --> 40:19.015
<i>[Ontreon] So no matter what
that scale says,</i>

40:19.017 --> 40:22.485
<i>I just pray that Dr. Now
can help me find some hope.</i>

40:25.589 --> 40:28.057
<i>Because I'm not ready
to just give up yet.</i>

40:37.067 --> 40:39.402
[suspenseful music playing]

40:43.574 --> 40:46.242
<i>[Ontreon] We're here at
