41:12.102 --> 41:14.070
<i>At least I lost something.</i>

41:14.705 --> 41:17.106
<i>But I guess I saw that coming.</i>

41:17.108 --> 41:19.075
- [laughing] - [nurse]
You can go to Room Five.

41:20.277 --> 41:23.046
Not even close,
but that's okay. [chuckles]

41:27.585 --> 41:29.319
[Musa laughs,
speaking indistinctly]

41:35.593 --> 41:39.562
- [speaking indistinctly] -
We're doing running now, but...

41:39.564 --> 41:41.197
[knocking at door]

41:44.068 --> 41:45.768
Hello, how are we all doing?

41:45.770 --> 41:49.873
- Good. How are you doing?
- Good.

41:49.875 --> 41:53.376
All right, uh, so, Ontreon,
what's going on with you?

41:53.378 --> 41:56.012
Because I see you lost
some weight, but not enough.

41:56.014 --> 41:57.981
So what happened?

41:57.983 --> 42:00.750
I didn't get to meet
necessarily the goal.

42:00.752 --> 42:05.421
Um, so I'm not too happy
about that. But, um...

42:06.457 --> 42:08.525
I think we're headed in--
