42:09.026 --> 42:10.193
Um...

42:10.694 --> 42:12.662
I just gotta do... Do better.

42:12.664 --> 42:16.933
I got a feeling that you're really
sugarcoating what you have done.

42:16.935 --> 42:19.002
All right, I'm...
I don't think you've really,

42:19.004 --> 42:20.770
uh, done much of the diet

42:20.772 --> 42:22.805
except maybe one or two days.

42:22.807 --> 42:25.975
I don't think you really have
done any of this exercise,

42:25.977 --> 42:27.176
maybe five minutes.

42:27.178 --> 42:29.779
So you're not
taking this seriously

42:29.781 --> 42:32.849
and making excuses
not to be healthy

42:32.851 --> 42:36.819
and do the right thing with
your diet and your exercise.

42:36.821 --> 42:40.790
And then, all you did
was you made some changes

42:40.792 --> 42:42.926
but not a lot of changes.

42:42.928 --> 42:46.262
So what changes
do you think you make?

42:47.031 --> 42:48.164
Um...

42:48.166 --> 42:51.134
I've really been trying to,
uh, stick with the, um,

42:51.136 --> 42:55.138
1,200 calorie, um, diet,
um, per day.

42:55.573 --> 42:56.806
Um... [clears throat]

42:56.808 --> 42:58.074
I know that we...
Me and my wife,

42:58.076 --> 43:00.910
we discussed about
protein shakes.

43:00.912 --> 43:03.880
And I know that I've been
drinking some protein shakes.

43:03.882 --> 43:07.984
And she's been on to me about that
because she said they wouldn't... I'm not--

43:07.986 --> 43:10.286
What do you mean? You're
drinking protein shakes?

43:11.288 --> 43:12.355
Yes.

43:12.690 --> 43:14.657
Okay.

43:14.659 --> 43:17.694
You have eaten the food that
belongs to the next five years.

43:17.696 --> 43:20.063
How in the world
do you need a protein shake?

43:20.065 --> 43:23.132
What do you need
to take a protein shake for?

43:24.735 --> 43:26.336
Who gave you that idea?

43:28.939 --> 43:31.407
I don't know. I just...
I just... I don't know.

43:32.076 --> 43:33.943
Well, I though it was because,
you know,

43:33.945 --> 43:36.179
- I was low on calories-- - What
do you mean you don't know?

43:36.181 --> 43:38.748
We gave you stuff to read
and that said that

43:38.750 --> 43:40.984
no supplements, no shakes.

43:40.986 --> 43:43.186
Tell me, did you read
the stuff I gave you?

43:43.188 --> 43:45.922
Uh, I did read...
I did read some of it.

43:45.924 --> 43:47.991
Um, I haven't--
I haven't read it all.

43:47.993 --> 43:52.862
Well, you have to understand
what to do, what not to do.

43:52.864 --> 43:55.098
So I'm not going to ask you
any questions. Let me ask her.

43:55.100 --> 43:56.833
[chuckles]

43:56.835 --> 44:00.436
Do you think Ontreon was doing
he was supposed to be doing

44:00.438 --> 44:02.171
and sticking to the diet?

44:02.173 --> 44:05.975
Um... Like, the first day
he was doing good.

44:05.977 --> 44:08.945
Like, the first three days?

44:08.947 --> 44:12.081
And then
he started having the shakes.

44:12.083 --> 44:14.951
Then I told him it says in
the book, don't take them.

44:14.953 --> 44:18.788
And then he said, "No.
I used to take them before."

44:18.790 --> 44:21.391
I'm like, "You know,
before, you did take them,

44:21.393 --> 44:24.193
whatever, but the diet says
no shakes.

44:24.795 --> 44:26.062
No shakes at all."

44:26.064 --> 44:31.801
But he made up an argument.
I just left him to be.

44:31.803 --> 44:35.838
And then the other day,
he was eating peanut butter.

44:35.840 --> 44:37.640
He said it's there
in the book that

44:37.642 --> 44:38.675
he must eat peanut butter.

44:38.677 --> 44:41.144
I said, "I read it.
